           05 VALUE ALL " " PIC X(095) LINE 26 COL 01.
           05 INSTRUCTIONS-TEXT LINE 25 COL 03 PIC X(085)
               FOREGROUND-COLOR 4 BACKGROUND-COLOR 7.
